So it turns out Bahn-sama was
a real villain all along, huh?

rows.label: tlk45450111_05_msg0002
rows.name: I can't believe this is happening...

rows.label: tlk45450111_05_msg0003
rows.name:
To add insult to injury, I managed
to hurt my leg pretty bad.

rows.label: tlk45450111_05_msg0004
rows.name:
It really feels like the happy times
are just a distant memory already.

rows.label: tlk45450111_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Ugh... This is all Harghal's fault,
I know it is. That dirty traitor!
